{{Infobox journal | editor = Michael T. Klein | discipline = [[Chemistry]], [[fossil fuel]]s | abbreviation = Energy Fuels | publisher = [[American Chemical Society]] | country = United States | frequency = Monthly | history = 1987-present | impact = 3.091 | impact-year = 2016 | website = http://pubs.acs.org/journal/enfuem | link1 = http://pubs.acs.org/toc/enfuem/current | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://pubs.acs.org/loi/enfuem | link2-name = Online archive | cover =ef cover.jpg | image_size =200px | CODEN = ENFUEM | ISSN = 0887-0624 | eISSN = 1520-5029 | OCLC = 13076751 | LCCN = 87658131 }} '''''Energy & Fuels''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] published by the [[American Chemical Society]]. It was established in 1987. Its publication frequency switched from bimonthly to monthly in 2009. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Michael T. Klein ([[University of Delaware]]).
